@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pawtok(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = ((v1 / wp.sin(v1 + 0.07)) * 0.09)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.86 * v0 + 0.82)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.76)) * ((tmp + 0.87 / v1 + 0.41) + 0.57))
    v2 = (v0 * wp.exp(0.46))
    v0 = 0.79
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.40 / v2 + 0.76)) + ((v0 + 0.45 + v2 + 0.23) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.70)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
